-- Bank of America close to settling on credit cards with U.S. regulator 
-- 
-- Thu Apr 03, 2014 05:16PM EDT
-- None



WASHINGTON, April 3 (Reuters) - Bank of America Corp <BAC.N> is close to a settlement with the U.S. Consumer Financial Protection Bureau over problems with products sold as add-ons to credit cards, sources familiar with the talks said.

